Link:

https://acloudxpert.com/how-to-install-terraform-on-amazon-linux-ami-ec2/

1. Download Terraform:
  wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.4.2/terraform_1.4.2_linux_amd64.zip
  
2. Check where to unzip package

3. Find out executable path
   echo $PATH
   unzip terraform_1.4.2_linux_amd64.zip -d /usr/bin/
   
4. Verify Installation
   terraform -v
